        <Parent_String>Greek sculpture styles [300020205], Aegean sculpture styles [300107032], Aegean styles [300106921], Aegean [300020059], Mediterranean (Early Western World) [300020058], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
